  "text": "where OFDM is the orthogonal frequency division multiplexing (OFDM) symbol duration, Tx = K OFDM , and K is the total number of transmit OFDM time intervals for the considered duty cycle. The total allocated bandwidth for RB for UE served by BS is , . The average capacity over a duty cycle period is used as a performance measure in this study as in [CITATION_1] . The DL capacity of LTE-U BS is given as",
